description:
This is a 5 minute workout called '5 min Cardio HIIT Workout for Fat Loss - 40s/20s Intervals - Home Workouts' from the channel Group HIIT.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Follow this quick HIIT workout for intense cardio and calorie burn. This workout uses bodyweight movements to get your heart rate up and burn calories. Try 3-4 rounds for a full workout. For more workouts, go to GroupHIIT.com. Follow our day by day workout programs from home. This workout requires no equipment!
